	<div style="font-size: 1.4em; margin: 60px 0 80px;">
		<h2>How to fix?</h2>
    <div style="text-align: left; width: 750px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <div style="float: left; width: 375px;">
        <h3>Python</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Your app should listen on IP 0.0.0.0 and port defined in <code>os.getenv('PORT')</code></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div style="float: left; width: 375px;">
        <h3>Node.js</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Make sure your package.json defines the <a href="https://docs.npmjs.com/misc/scripts" target="_blank">start script</a> or the file <b>app.js</b> is your main script</li>
          <li>Your app should listen on IP 0.0.0.0 and port defined in <code>process.env.PORT</code></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div style="clear:both"></div>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: left; width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
